<placeName cert="high">Phil&lt;Alexandria</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ἀμύντας Ἀπολλωνίωι 

    <lb n="2"/>χαίρειν. εἰ ἔρρωσαι, εὖ ἂν 

    <lb n="3"/>ἔχοι· ἔρρωμαι δὲ καὶ αὐτός. 

    <lb n="4"/>ἠξίωσεν ἡμᾶς Μένανδρος 

    <lb n="5"/>ὁ παρ᾽ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">Ἡ</unclear>ρακ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λ</unclear>είδου γράψαι σοι 

    <lb n="6"/>ἵνα περὶ ὧν ἀποδεδήμηκεν 

    <lb n="7"/>πρὸς σὲ ἐντύχηι σαυτῶι 

    <lb n="8"/>εὐ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κα</unclear>ίρως. καλῶς ἂν οὖν 

    <lb n="9"/>πο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ιή</unclear>σαις δοὺς αὐτῶι 

    <lb n="10"/>σαυτὸν εὐκαίρως. ὅμοιος 

    <lb n="11"/>γά<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρ ἐ</supplied>στιν ἄνθρωπος 

    <lb n="12"/>φρ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ον</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τίζ</unclear>οντι ὑπ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὲ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρ</unclear> σοῦ. 

    <lb n="13"/>ἔρρωσο. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="14"/>Ἀμύντου 

    <lb n="15"/>περὶ Μενάνδρου 

    <lb n="14"/>Ἀπολλωνίωι. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.706" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.706" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date type="textDate">Anfang 257 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.706" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Zen.</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">59046</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">706</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0092</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">59046</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0092;1;59046" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.706" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.706" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Alexandria</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.706" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://ipap.csad.ox.ac.uk/4DLink4/4DACTION/IPAPwebquery?vPub=P.Cair.Zen.&amp;vVol=1&amp;vNum=59046"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>